1
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:03,000
Master Bruce?

2
00:00:03,880 --> 00:00:06,140
Are you... all right, sir?

3
00:00:06,880 --> 00:00:08,320
I'm tired, Alfred.

4
00:00:08,680 --> 00:00:09,760
I shouldn't wonder.

5
00:00:10,080 --> 00:00:11,880
You've taken no meals today.

6
00:00:12,180 --> 00:00:14,220
I can't recall when you last slept.

7
00:00:15,100 --> 00:00:17,360
A weary body can be dealt with.

8
00:00:17,820 --> 00:00:20,940
But a weary spirit... that's something
else.

9
00:00:27,660 --> 00:00:31,380
Sometimes, old friend, I wonder if I'm
really doing any good out there.

10
00:00:31,381 --> 00:00:33,600
How can you doubt it?

11
00:00:33,820 --> 00:00:35,500
The lives you've saved?

12
00:00:35,501 --> 00:00:37,800
The criminals you've brought to justice?

13
00:00:38,140 --> 00:00:39,980
I've put out a few fires, yes.

14
00:00:40,400 --> 00:00:41,520
Won a few battles.

15
00:00:41,960 --> 00:00:43,960
But the war goes on, Alfred.

16
00:00:44,620 --> 00:00:45,920
On and on.

17
00:00:50,230 --> 00:00:51,410
You have it, Alfred?

18
00:00:52,270 --> 00:00:53,390
Of course, sir.

